d_matt_petrol_blue_web_6.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Arise_Geared_matt_petrol_blue_web_6.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Arise_Geared_matt_petrol_blue_web_6.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Arise_Geared_matt_petrol_blue_web_6.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Arise_Geared_matt_petrol_blue_web_6.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Arise_Geared_matt_petrol_blue_web_6.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Arise_Geared_matt_petrol_blue_web_6.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Arise_Geared_matt_petrol_blue_web_6.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.bombtrack.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bombtrack’s 2024 Lineup</a></h3>\n<p>One bike brand that has its finger on the pulse of competitive and non-competitive cyclists alike is Bombtrack. John loved the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2022-bombtrack-beyond-2-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Beyond 2 touring bike</a> and the brand’s Arise and Cale models have been popular over the years. For this launch, Bombtrack rolled out some real gems. The Oxbridge, Munroe Cargo, and Arise are all suited to commuting and cargo…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Hook_EXT_TI_titanium_black_web_1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Hook_EXT_TI_titanium_black_web_1.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Hook_EXT_TI_titanium_black_web_1.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavi