=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BT_MY24_Beyond_2_metallic_green_web_10.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>The Beyond got a refresh and the Hook Titanium and Cale look great for quicker-pace riding. We’re really blown away not at the bikes, but the studio photography by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/fwdbound/\" target=\"_blank\">Jason Sellers</a> as well! Feast your eyes upon <a href=\"https://www.bombtrack.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bombtrack’s new 2024 lineup</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"744\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_103122.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_103122.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_103122.jpg?resize=1024,635&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_103122.jpg?resize=768,476&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_103122.jpg?resize=700,434&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"751\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/CopyofBedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/CopyofBedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_1.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/CopyofBedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_1.jpg?resize=1024,641&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/CopyofBedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_1.jpg?resize=768,481&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/CopyofBedrockMT22_BydlonAndrew_1.jpg?resize=700,438&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"754\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BEDROCK_2023_090423_BydlonAndrew.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BEDROCK_2023_090423_BydlonAndrew.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BEDROCK_2023_090423_BydlonAndrew.jpg?resize=1024,643&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BEDROCK_2023_090423_BydlonAndrew.jpg?resize=768,483&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/BEDROCK_2023_090423_BydlonAndrew.jpg?resize=700,440&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://bedrocksandals.com/collections/bedrock-mountain-clogs\" target=\"_blank\">Bedrock Mountain Clogs Back in Stock</a> $160/$175</h3>\n<p>After its last shipment was stolen from Los Angeles en route to Montana, Bedrock finally has its popular Mountain Clogs back in stock in either Synthetic Suede, Nubuck Leather, and Leather Suede. These slide-on clogs feature a heal strap to hold the shoe on your foot and feature Vibram soles to keep your footing secure on slick surfaces.</p>\n<p>Check out the full Mountain Clog lineup at <a href=\"https://bedrocksandals.com/collections/bedrock-mountain-clogs\" target=\"_blank\">Bedrock</a>.</p>\n<p><em>See Spencer’s review here:</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bedrock-mountain-clog-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Bedrock Clogs Review: For Those Squeamish of Stubbing Their Toes</a></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/7732f27d-4fb2-41a3-9aaa-58783b69.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/7732f27d-4fb2-41a3-9aaa-58783b69.jpg?w=1500&amp;quality=75 1500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/7732f27d-4fb2-41a3-9aaa-58783b69.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/7732f27d-4fb2-41a3-9aaa-58783b69.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/7732f27d-4fb2-41a3-9aaa-58783b69.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/7732f27d-4fb2-41a3-9aaa-58783b69.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/7732f27d-4fb2-41a3-9aaa-58783b69.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/32686bb6-21f4-47df-b07f-1123e164.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/32686bb6-21f4-47df-b07f-1123e164.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/32686bb6-21f4-47df-b07f-1123e164.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/32686bb6-21f4-47df-b07f-1123e164.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/32686bb6-21f4-47df-b07f-1123e164.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.revelatedesigns.com/index.cfm/store.catalog/handlebar/pronghorn\" target=\"_blank\">The Return of the Revelate Pronghorn</a></h3>\n<p>It’s back and better than ever! The Pronghorn is Revelate’s race focused, lightweight handlebar system for the minimalist bikepacker. Without sacrificing functionality, the Pronghorn is a stripped-down bar mounted carrying system. A key to the system’s performance is a strategically placed internal fiberglass stay that is integrated into both the mounting points and front drybag attachment straps. This keeps your load from shifting while navigating technical singletrack.</p>\n<p>The latest Pronghorn update can be found in the drybag. The design is now double-ended, allowing for easier access to the contents of your bag! Made from Challenge Ultra 200 UHMWPE this waterproof bag comes in three sizes to fit every kind of adventure. Please note that in order to retain full waterproof functionality you’ll need to roll the ends of the drybag at least three times.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://www.revelatedesigns.com/index.cfm/store.catalog/handlebar/pronghorn\" target=\"_blank\">Revelate</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/4B95FC73-3718-4EBC-888F-26544ECD.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/4B95FC73-3718-4EBC-888F-26544ECD.jpg?w=1500&amp;quality=75 1500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/4B95FC73-3718-4EBC-888F-26544ECD.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/4B95FC73-3718-4EBC-888F-26544ECD.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/4B95FC73-3718-4EBC-888F-26544ECD.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/4B95FC73-3718-4EBC-888F-26544ECD.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9AADD3BD-4394-4639-950A-234A69FF.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9AADD3BD-4394-4639-950A-234A69FF.jpg?w=1500&amp;quality=75 1500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9AADD3BD-4394-4639-950A-234A69FF.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9AADD3BD-4394-4639-950A-234A69FF.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9AADD3BD-4394-4639-950A-234A69FF.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9AADD3BD-4394-4639-950A-234A69FF.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1273\" height=\"849\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9C23AB9C-5793-40F9-B828-A7A2733F.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9C23AB9C-5793-40F9-B828-A7A2733F.jpg?w=1273&amp;quality=75 1273w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9C23AB9C-5793-40F9-B828-A7A2733F.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9C23AB9C-5793-40F9-B828-A7A2733F.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/9C23AB9C-5793-40F9-B828-A7A2733F.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.thisisfarewell.com/store/p/scout-roll?fbclid=PAAabemdHBrQCBP-CUJIFXWJFjXVfN_vWWPNadbW9-rn2Qxv4BzYR2OdHk7Y0_aem_Afhf9bHAnA2sfcvLEBwf6Nh4l4WrgICF8cwfStcFHg6ofsydy5yiZy0ALSU3XQA7Qj0\" target=\"_blank\">Farewell Scout Roll – Made to Order</a> $50</h3>\n<p>A multi-purpose organizer that makes a great first aid or med-kit, tool pouch or skin care kit for climbers. The Scout Roll is an organizer that utilizes a magnetic buckle for quick deployment and mesh pockets so you can easily see contents and get to only what ya need. Perfect for a gravel/MTB tool kit or for keeping your bike touring essentials organized and neat. Features a webbing loop for hanging from a tree for your trailside repair or an anchor on a wall to tend to your shredded skin or wounds.</p>\n<p>Size is 6”H x 14”L. Weight is ~3oz.</p>\n<p>Please allow 1-2 weeks for production and shipping. This is a made to order item. Check out more at <a href=\"https://www.thisisfarewell.com/store/p/scout-roll?fbclid=PAAabemdHBrQCBP-CUJIFXWJFjXVfN_vWWPNadbW9-rn2Qxv4BzYR2OdHk7Y0_aem_Afhf9bHAnA2sfcvLEBwf6Nh4l4WrgICF8cwfStcFHg6ofsydy5yiZy0ALSU3XQA7Qj0\" target=\"_blank\">Farewell</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/WW_HIP-PACK_RUST_ORANGE_BOTTLE_G.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/WW_HIP-PACK_RUST_ORANGE_BOTTLE_G.jpg?w=1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/WW_HIP-PACK_RUST_ORANGE_BOTTLE_G.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/WW_HIP-PACK_RUST_ORANGE_BOTTLE_G.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/WW_HIP-PACK_RUST_ORANGE_BOTTLE_G.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/WW_HIP-PACK_RUST_ORANGE_BOTTLE_G.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/wizard_works_hobgob_hip_pack_bot.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/wizard_works_hobgob_hip_pack_bot.jpg?w=1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/wizard_works_hobgob_hip_pack_bot.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/wizard_works_hobgob_hip_pack_bot.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/wizard_works_hobgob_hip_pack_bot.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/wizard_works_hobgob_hip_pack_bot.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wizard.works/shop/accessories/accessories-brands/wizard-works/quick-draw-bottle-pocket/\" target=\"_blank\">Wizard Works Quick Draw Bottle Pocket</a> £30</h3>\n<p>The Quick Draw Bottle Pocket can be attached to Wizard Works’ Hobgob Hip Pack allowing you to carry a water bottle. The structured shape allows for one handed access to your bottle whilst riding, and the elastic strap will secure your bidon over the rowdiest of trails.</p>\n<p>Two Blackhawk Speed Clips are provided for attaching the Bottle Pocket, which are woven through the webbing onto the wing of the Hip Pack.</p>\n<p>Made in-house, London, UK and shipping from <a href=\"https://www.wizard.works/shop/accessories/accessories-brands/wizard-works/quick-draw-bottle-pocket/\" target=\"_blank\">Wizard Works</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1249\" height=\"832\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/280231-Steve-Potts-Cycles-Siskiy.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/280231-Steve-Potts-Cycles-Siskiy.jpg?w=1249&amp;quality=75 1249w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/280231-Steve-Potts-Cycles-Siskiy.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/280231-Steve-Potts-Cycles-Siskiy.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/280231-Steve-Potts-Cycles-Siskiy.jpg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.somafabshop.com/shop/steve-potts-cycles-siskiyou-handlebar-crmo-twn-7722#attr=3270,4729,1854\" target=\"_blank\">Steve Potts Cycles Siskiyou CrMo Handlebar</a> $ 99.95</h3>\n<p>Previously only available as a titanium handmade bar by the master himself, Steve Potts, these new Siskiyou CrMo Handlebar are now made in Taiwan at a much more affordable pricepoint. Because the Nitto factory in Japan was backed up during the pandemic, these were made in Taiwan. Care was taken to replicate the dull nickel finish that Nitto is known for. These bars are perfect for a rigid MTB or touring bike where you want the control of a flat bar with more hand positions.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Satin nickel-plated finish or painted Black</li>\n<li>Width: 760mm c-c</li>\n<li>Backsweep/Grip angle: 30°</li>\n<li>Reach of horns: 80mm</li>\n<li>Reachback: 72mm</li>\n<li>Center: 25.4mm or 31.8mm</li>\n<li>Weight: 820g (25.4mm), 750g (31.8mm)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In stock at <a href=\"https://www.somafabshop.com/shop/steve-potts-cycles-siskiyou-handlebar-crmo-twn-7722#attr=3270,4729,1854\" target=\"_blank\">SOMA</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Bender-Bicycle-Co-Commuter-Bike-4.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Bender-Bicycle-Co-Commuter-Bike-4.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Bender-Bicycle-Co-Commuter-Bike-4.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Bender-Bicycle-Co-Commuter-Bike-4.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Bender-Bicycle-Co-Commuter-Bike-4.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Bender-Bicycle-Co-Commuter-Bike-4.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Bender-Bicycle-Co-Commuter-Bike-4.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Bender-Bicycle-Co-Commuter-Bike-4.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Cyx_yFcuxnt/?igshid=MTc4MmM1YmI2Ng%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\">Bender Bicycles is Selling its MADE Show Bike</a> $6000</h3>\n<p>Rigid mountain bikes are multi-purpose, capable rigs! This Bender was featured in our MADE Bike Show coverage and is currently for sale, heavily discounted:</p>\n<p><em>“This was a show bike I built for MADE. It is brand new and has never been ridden. It is built up with all the best parts from the best brands in the industry. This bike is a size large of my  “Master of None” model.</em></p>\n<p><em>In short, it’s a bike designed to be adapted to ride whatever is in front of you. The current build kit leans towards commuter mode, but take the fenders and rack off, and you can rip some single track, or throw bags on it for a tour.</em></p>\n<p><em>This bike has tons of premium parts (list in bio), so don’t sleep on this killer deal. Message with any questions!”</em></p>\n<p>Hit up Bender on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Cyx_yFcuxnt/?igshid=MTc4MmM1YmI2Ng%3D%3D\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/e8efdcdf-796c-4593-9d89-114ea797-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/8545964a-72bc-4514-8986-8c2b25f7-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2114\" height=\"1409\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?w=2114&amp;quality=75 2114w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/40db2822-fc40-413f-988f-9f6b5100.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3>Rad Bazaar Finds</h3>\n<p><em>We love seeing the support for our Rad Bazaar, a service we host for Group Ride members. For now, you can read all about how to sign up for the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/the-radavist-group-ride-subscription-plan-and-rad-bazaar/\" target=\"_blank\">Group Ride and Rad Bazaar here</a>.</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://radbazaar.theradavist.com/listing/FtTE6ZdeRWb9KLZUsIYr?category=undefined&amp;subcategory=undefined\" target=\"_blank\">Yellow Acoustic Cargo Bike $500</a></p>\n<p>Weird custom cargo bike, unknown builder but nice and yellow. Front basket area fits a 55qt cooler perfectly with a heavy duty topeak rear rack. I threw some Velo Orange Sienne bars on there with PNW grips. Set up 1x right now with some decent range. 26” in the rear and 20”(451) in the front. Fits in between a medium and a large. Pick up in PDX only</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://radbazaar.theradavist.com/listing/YM1fN3Fr4hAmHtwrRpzi?category=undefined&amp;subcategory=undefined\" target=\"_blank\">Fujifilm X100f Digital Camera $950</a></p>\n<p>I had high hopes of using this perfectly sized camera on bike rides and tours, but mostly reach for my larger cameras instead. Other than a few signs of use on the outer housing, this X100f is in excellent condition – both the lens and screen are nearly perfect. Two batteries and lens cap are included. Check the full specs over at <a href=\"https://www.bhphotovideo.com/c/product/1311229-REG/fujifilm_16534584_x100f_camera_silver.html\" target=\"_blank\">B&amp;H</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://radbazaar.theradavist.com/listing/dCXWGGSTa9BayKxo3edl?category=bikes&amp;subcategory=undefined\" target=\"_blank\">Specialized Stumpjumper ATB $550</a></p>\n<p>Coolest stumpy around. Snag it before someone else does. It’s got all you need, comfy bars, dynamo hub and headlight, front rack, quality parts. Frame: 1987 Stumpjumper size 21 Stem: Nitto Technomic Bars: Nitto Rivendell Bosco Shifter: Suntour Power Thumb Brake Lever: Dia Compe XCE Grip: Oury Brown RR Wheel: Satura GX26/ Specialized FT Wheel: Satura GX26/ SP Dynamo Tires: Gravelking 2.1 RR Der: Suntour XC 9000 FT Der: Suntour XC 9000 Crank: Shimano FC-B124 FT Brake: BR-M160 RR Brake: BR-MT61 Seatpost: Strong Headlight: Kasai Trail Beam Rack: Pelago Looking for a rad used bike? Follow @hobohubworks on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hobohubworks\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> or <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hobohubworks\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<div><span><span>﻿</span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3UTooSGFWTQ\" target=\"_blank\">Tesekkür, Turkey – A Cycling Film by Restrap</a></h3>\n<p>Restrap doesn’t just make bikepacking bags and cycling accessories. The brand also lives and breathes bikepacking. Every year the Restrap team plans a big tour that allows them to shakedown their bags and look for ways in which the design team can improve them.</p>\n<p>This tour would take us along the Aegean coastline from Dalaman in the south, through the mountain ranges surrounding Izmir and finishing at the historic city of Istanbul.</p>\n<p>Full route for this tour can be found at <a href=\"https://www.komoot.com/tour/1248901441\" target=\"_blank\">Komoot</a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><span><span>﻿</span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwih-r6EUto\" target=\"_blank\">Cerro Gordo</a></h3>\n<p>We’re slowly uploading our YouTube content back to <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@theradavist666\" target=\"_blank\">The Radavist’s YouTube channel</a>, today we’re sharing our Cerro Gordo film John made with SRAM and James Adamson back in 2019.</p>\n<p><em><strong>See our Reportage from the project here:</strong></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://theradavist.com/up-into-the-inyo-mountains-disconnecting-in-cerro-gordo/\" target=\"_blank\">Into the Inyo Mountains: Disconnecting in Cerro Gordo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cerro-gordo-excursion-disconnecting-with-a-sram-axs-equipped-moots-baxter/\" target=\"_blank\">Disconnecting with a SRAM AXS Equipped Moots Baxter</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Radavision</h3>\n<p>Stuff we see on the ‘net that causes pause…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2019/02/CERROGORDO-82.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2019/02/CERROGORDO-82.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2019/02/CERROGORDO-82.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2019/02/CERROGORDO-82.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2019/02/CERROGORDO-82.jpg?resize=1900,1266&amp;quality=75 1900w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2019/02/CERROGORDO-82.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2019/02/CERROGORDO-82.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/johnprolly/\" target=\"_blank\">@johnprolly</a></em></p>\n<p>We thought it’d be fitting with the re-sharing of our Cerro Gordo project with SRAM to share one of the many landscapes John captured on that project…</p>\n<p><em>If you’d like your photo featured in our Radar Roundup posts, tag us <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theradavist/\" target=\"_blank\">on Instagram</a>!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-bombtrack-2023-lineup-revelate-pronghorn-returns-farewell-scout-roll-wizard-works-quick-draw-bottle-pocket-steve-potts-bars-bender-made-show-bike/\">Radar Roundup: Bombtrack 2023 Lineup, Bedrock Mountain Clogs, Revelate Pronghorn Returns, Farewell Scout Roll, Wizard Works Quick Draw Bottle Pocket, Steve Potts Bars, Bender MADE Show Bike, and Tesekkür Turkey</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"a619470d1e1007fc0f255784c414034bc5f9f74bc852df6fce58430be4f70c1f","category":"Cycling"}